{
  "video_id": "VfAiNX7jn9A",
  "title": "The unexpected challenges of a country's first election | Philippa Neave",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12920.0,
      "end_time": 15719.0,
      "text": "The great philosopher Aristotle said"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16840.0,
      "end_time": 20320.0,
      "text": "if something doesn&#39;t exist, there&#39;s no word for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21320.0,
      "end_time": 23776.0,
      "text": "and if there&#39;s no word for something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23800.0,
      "end_time": 25440.0,
      "text": "that something doesn&#39;t exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26200.0,
      "end_time": 28335.0,
      "text": "So when we talk about elections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28360.0,
      "end_time": 31936.0,
      "text": "we in established democracies, we know what we&#39;re talking about."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31960.0,
      "end_time": 34560.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got the words. We have the vocabulary."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34800.0,
      "end_time": 35976.0,
      "text": "We know what a polling station is."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36000.0,
      "end_time": 37720.0,
      "text": "We know what a ballot paper is."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38840.0,
      "end_time": 42720.0,
      "text": "But what about countries where democracy doesn&#39;t exist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43760.0,
      "end_time": 48560.0,
      "text": "countries where there are no words to describe the concepts"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48800.0,
      "end_time": 50519.0,
      "text": "that underpin a democratic society?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51560.0,
      "end_time": 53856.0,
      "text": "I work in the field of electoral assistance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53880.0,
      "end_time": 56160.0,
      "text": "so that&#39;s to say we assist"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56400.0,
      "end_time": 58176.0,
      "text": "emerging democracies to organize"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58200.0,
      "end_time": 60800.0,
      "text": "what is often their first elections."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61480.0,
      "end_time": 62895.0,
      "text": "When people ask me what I do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62920.0,
      "end_time": 65336.0,
      "text": "quite often I get this answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65360.0,
      "end_time": 69176.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, so you&#39;re one of these people who goes around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69200.0,
      "end_time": 73120.0,
      "text": "imposing Western democracy on countries that can&#39;t handle it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74480.0,
      "end_time": 78840.0,
      "text": "Well, the United Nations does not impose anything on anybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79600.0,
      "end_time": 80815.0,
      "text": "It really doesn&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 80840.0,
      "end_time": 83216.0,
      "text": "and also, what we do"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 83240.0,
      "end_time": 89536.0,
      "text": "is firmly anchored in the 1948 Universal Declaration of Human Rights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89560.0,
      "end_time": 91656.0,
      "text": "Article 21, that says"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91680.0,
      "end_time": 95200.0,
      "text": "that everybody should have the right to choose who governs them."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96000.0,
      "end_time": 97536.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s the basis of the work."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97560.0,
      "end_time": 100456.0,
      "text": "I specialize in public outreach."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100480.0,
      "end_time": 102896.0,
      "text": "What does that mean? Another jargon."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102920.0,
      "end_time": 106696.0,
      "text": "It actually means designing information campaigns"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 106720.0,
      "end_time": 109136.0,
      "text": "so that candidates and voters"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109160.0,
      "end_time": 113456.0,
      "text": "who have never had the opportunity to participate or to vote"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 113480.0,
      "end_time": 117216.0,
      "text": "understand where, when, how to register;"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117240.0,
      "end_time": 119455.0,
      "text": "where, when, how to vote;"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 119480.0,
      "end_time": 122000.0,
      "text": "why, why it is important to take part."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 122560.0,
      "end_time": 127160.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ll probably devise a specific campaign to reach out to women"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 127400.0,
      "end_time": 129560.0,
      "text": "to make sure that they can take part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 129800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131376.0,
      "text": "that they can be part of the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 131400.0,
      "end_time": 133256.0,
      "text": "Young people as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 133280.0,
      "end_time": 134496.0,
      "text": "All sorts of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134520.0,
      "end_time": 135936.0,
      "text": "Handicapped people."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 135960.0,
      "end_time": 137560.0,
      "text": "We try to reach everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 138800.0,
      "end_time": 142256.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not always easy, because very often in this work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 142280.0,
      "end_time": 145416.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve noticed now over the years that I&#39;ve been doing it"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 145440.0,
      "end_time": 147856.0,
      "text": "that words are lacking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 147880.0,
      "end_time": 149519.0,
      "text": "and so what do you do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 150120.0,
      "end_time": 151320.0,
      "text": "Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 152200.0,
      "end_time": 154696.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a country with high levels of illiteracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 154720.0,
      "end_time": 158576.0,
      "text": "and the thing about that was, it was in 2005,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 158600.0,
      "end_time": 162576.0,
      "text": "and we organized two elections on the same day."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 162600.0,
      "end_time": 166816.0,
      "text": "The reason was because the logistics are so incredibly difficult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 166840.0,
      "end_time": 169960.0,
      "text": "it seemed to be more efficient to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 169120.0,
      "end_time": 170336.0,
      "text": "It was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 170360.0,
      "end_time": 174816.0,
      "text": "but on the other hand, explaining two elections instead of one"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 174840.0,
      "end_time": 176336.0,
      "text": "was even more complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 176360.0,
      "end_time": 178696.0,
      "text": "So we used a lot of images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 178720.0,
      "end_time": 181520.0,
      "text": "and when it came to the actual ballot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 182360.0,
      "end_time": 185456.0,
      "text": "we had problems, because so many people wanted to take part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 185480.0,
      "end_time": 190416.0,
      "text": "we had 300 candidates for 52 seats"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 190440.0,
      "end_time": 193480.0,
      "text": "in the Wolesi Jirga, which is the parliamentary elections."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 194000.0,
      "end_time": 197216.0,
      "text": "And for the Provincial Council, we had even more candidates."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 197240.0,
      "end_time": 199800.0,
      "text": "We had 330 for 54 seats."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 200240.0,
      "end_time": 202520.0,
      "text": "So talking about ballot design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 203320.0,
      "end_time": 206640.0,
      "text": "this is what the ballot looked like."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 207600.0,
      "end_time": 209216.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the size of a newspaper."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 209240.0,
      "end_time": 211000.0,
      "text": "This was the Wolesi Jirga ballot --"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 211426.0,
      "end_time": 212576.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 212600.0,
      "end_time": 213960.0,
      "text": "Yeah, and --"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 215800.0,
      "end_time": 218800.0,
      "text": "this was the Provincial Council ballot."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 219400.0,
      "end_time": 220696.0,
      "text": "Even more."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 220720.0,
      "end_time": 225656.0,
      "text": "So you see, we did use a lot of symbols and things like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 225680.0,
      "end_time": 230456.0,
      "text": "And we had other problems in Southern Sudan."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 230480.0,
      "end_time": 233215.0,
      "text": "Southern Sudan was a very different story."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 233240.0,
      "end_time": 236336.0,
      "text": "We had so many people who had never, of course, voted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 236360.0,
      "end_time": 240160.0,
      "text": "but we had extremely, extremely high levels of illiteracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 241120.0,
      "end_time": 242896.0,
      "text": "very, very poor infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 242920.0,
      "end_time": 247495.0,
      "text": "For example -- I mean, it&#39;s a country the size of Texas, more or less."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 247520.0,
      "end_time": 250400.0,
      "text": "We had seven kilometers of paved roads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 251280.0,
      "end_time": 253336.0,
      "text": "seven kilometers in the whole country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 253360.0,
      "end_time": 256496.0,
      "text": "and that includes the tarmac where we landed the planes"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 256519.0,
      "end_time": 258550.0,
      "text": "in Juba Airport."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 258790.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261216.00000000003,
      "text": "So transporting electoral materials, etc.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 261240.0,
      "end_time": 263496.0,
      "text": "is exceedingly difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 263520.0,
      "end_time": 268495.0,
      "text": "People had no idea about what a box looked like."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 268519.0,
      "end_time": 270815.0,
      "text": "It was very complicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 270839.0,
      "end_time": 274936.0,
      "text": "so using verbal communication was obviously the way to go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 274960.0,
      "end_time": 277960.0,
      "text": "but there were 132 languages."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 278800.0,
      "end_time": 281720.0,
      "text": "So that was extremely challenging."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 282480.0,
      "end_time": 286336.0,
      "text": "Then I arrived in Tunisia in 2011."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 286360.0,
      "end_time": 288160.0,
      "text": "It was the Arab Spring."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 288400.0,
      "end_time": 292336.0,
      "text": "A huge amount of hope was generated by that enormous movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 292360.0,
      "end_time": 293936.0,
      "text": "that was going on in the region."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 293960.0,
      "end_time": 297960.0,
      "text": "There was Libya, there was Egypt, there was Yemen."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 297120.0,
      "end_time": 300136.0,
      "text": "It was an enormous, enormous historical moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 300160.0,
      "end_time": 302736.0,
      "text": "And I was sitting with the election commission,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 302760.0,
      "end_time": 306496.0,
      "text": "and we were talking about various aspects of the election,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 306520.0,
      "end_time": 309856.0,
      "text": "and I was hearing them using words that I hadn&#39;t actually heard before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 309880.0,
      "end_time": 314960.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d worked with Iraqis, I&#39;d worked with Jordanians, Egyptians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 314120.0,
      "end_time": 316536.0,
      "text": "and suddenly they were using these words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 316560.0,
      "end_time": 318416.0,
      "text": "and I just thought, \"This is strange.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 318440.0,
      "end_time": 321336.0,
      "text": "And what really gave rise to it was this word \"observer.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 321360.0,
      "end_time": 323616.0,
      "text": "We were discussing election observers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 323640.0,
      "end_time": 328455.0,
      "text": "and the election commissioner was talking about \"mulahiz\" in Arabic."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 328480.0,
      "end_time": 332576.0,
      "text": "This means \"to notice\" in a passive sort of sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 332600.0,
      "end_time": 336216.0,
      "text": "as in, \"I noticed he was wearing a light blue shirt.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 336240.0,
      "end_time": 339936.0,
      "text": "Did I go and check whether the shirt was light blue or not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 339960.0,
      "end_time": 341936.0,
      "text": "That is the role of an election observer."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 341960.0,
      "end_time": 346150.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very active, it&#39;s governed by all kinds of treaties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 346400.0,
      "end_time": 348816.0,
      "text": "and it has got that control function in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 348840.0,
      "end_time": 351150.0,
      "text": "And then I got wind of the fact that in Egypt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 351400.0,
      "end_time": 354376.0,
      "text": "they were using this term \"mutabiâ€™,\" which means \"to follow.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 354400.0,
      "end_time": 356695.0,
      "text": "So we were now having followers of an election."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 356720.0,
      "end_time": 359296.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s not quite right either,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 359320.0,
      "end_time": 362820.0,
      "text": "because there is a term that&#39;s already accepted and in use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 362106.0,
      "end_time": 365376.0,
      "text": "which was the word \"muraqib\" which means \"a controller.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 365400.0,
      "end_time": 367536.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s got that notion of control."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 367560.0,
      "end_time": 371296.0,
      "text": "So I thought, three words for one concept. This is not good."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 371320.0,
      "end_time": 374416.0,
      "text": "And with our colleagues, we thought perhaps it&#39;s our role"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 374440.0,
      "end_time": 378496.0,
      "text": "to actually help make sure that the words are understood"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 378520.0,
      "end_time": 381656.0,
      "text": "and actually create a work of reference"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 381680.0,
      "end_time": 384336.0,
      "text": "that could be used across the Arab region."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 384360.0,
      "end_time": 385616.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s what we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 385640.0,
      "end_time": 387296.0,
      "text": "So together with these colleagues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 387320.0,
      "end_time": 391296.0,
      "text": "we launched the \"Arabic Lexicon of Electoral Terminology,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 391320.0,
      "end_time": 393640.0,
      "text": "and we worked in eight different countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 394600.0,
      "end_time": 399176.0,
      "text": "It meant actually defining 481 terms"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 399200.0,
      "end_time": 402560.0,
      "text": "which formed the basis of everything you need to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 402800.0,
      "end_time": 404440.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;re going to organize a democratic election."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 404880.0,
      "end_time": 406216.0,
      "text": "And we defined these terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 406240.0,
      "end_time": 408216.0,
      "text": "and we worked with the Arab colleagues"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 408240.0,
      "end_time": 412160.0,
      "text": "and came to an agreement about what would be the appropriate word"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 412400.0,
      "end_time": 413616.0,
      "text": "to use in Arabic."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 413640.0,
      "end_time": 417895.0,
      "text": "Because the Arabic language is very rich, and that&#39;s part of the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 417920.0,
      "end_time": 420896.0,
      "text": "But there are 22 countries that speak Arabic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 420920.0,
      "end_time": 425616.0,
      "text": "and they use modern standard Arabic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 425640.0,
      "end_time": 428496.0,
      "text": "which is the Arabic that is used across the whole region"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 428520.0,
      "end_time": 431150.0,
      "text": "in newspapers and broadcasts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 431400.0,
      "end_time": 435936.0,
      "text": "but of course, then from one country to the next in day to day language and use"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 435970.0,
      "end_time": 439296.0,
      "text": "it varies -- dialect, colloquialisms, etc."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 439320.0,
      "end_time": 441896.0,
      "text": "So that was another added layer of complication."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 441920.0,
      "end_time": 444416.0,
      "text": "So in one sense you had the problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 444440.0,
      "end_time": 448960.0,
      "text": "that language wasn&#39;t fully ripe, if you like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 448120.0,
      "end_time": 450800.0,
      "text": "neologisms were coming up, new expressions."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 451400.0,
      "end_time": 453560.0,
      "text": "And so we defined all these terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 453800.0,
      "end_time": 456376.0,
      "text": "and then we had eight correspondents in the region."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 456400.0,
      "end_time": 458296.0,
      "text": "We submitted the draft to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 458320.0,
      "end_time": 459896.0,
      "text": "they responded back to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 459920.0,
      "end_time": 462536.0,
      "text": "\"Yes, we understand the definition."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 462560.0,
      "end_time": 464256.0,
      "text": "We agree with it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 464280.0,
      "end_time": 467455.0,
      "text": "but this is what we say in our country.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 467480.0,
      "end_time": 471960.0,
      "text": "Because we were not going to harmonize or force harmonization."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 471120.0,
      "end_time": 474120.0,
      "text": "We were trying to facilitate understanding among people."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 474640.0,
      "end_time": 479695.0,
      "text": "So in yellow, you see the different expressions in use"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 479720.0,
      "end_time": 481400.0,
      "text": "in the various countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 482000.0,
      "end_time": 485936.0,
      "text": "So this, I&#39;m happy to say, it took three years to produce this"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 485960.0,
      "end_time": 490296.0,
      "text": "because we also finalized the draft and took it actually into the field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 490320.0,
      "end_time": 493462.0,
      "text": "sat with the election commissions in all these different countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 493487.0,
      "end_time": 496376.0,
      "text": "debated and defined and refined the draft,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 496400.0,
      "end_time": 501416.0,
      "text": "and finally published it in November 2014 in Cairo."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 501440.0,
      "end_time": 504695.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s gone a long way. We published 10,000 copies."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 504720.0,
      "end_time": 509936.0,
      "text": "To date, there&#39;s about 3,000 downloads off the internet in PDF form."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 509960.0,
      "end_time": 513856.0,
      "text": "I heard just recently from a colleague that they&#39;ve taken it up in Somalia."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 513880.0,
      "end_time": 516775.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re going to produce a version of this in Somalia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 516799.0,
      "end_time": 518815.0,
      "text": "because there&#39;s nothing in Somalia at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 518840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521856.00000000006,
      "text": "So that&#39;s very good to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 521880.0,
      "end_time": 526135.0,
      "text": "And this newly formed Arab Organization for Electoral Management Bodies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 526159.0,
      "end_time": 529960.0,
      "text": "which is trying to professionalize"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 529120.0,
      "end_time": 531416.0,
      "text": "how elections are run in the region,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 531440.0,
      "end_time": 533535.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re using it as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 533559.0,
      "end_time": 539496.0,
      "text": "And the Arab League have now built up a pan-Arab observation unit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 539520.0,
      "end_time": 540776.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re using it."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 540800.0,
      "end_time": 543415.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s all really good."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 543440.0,
      "end_time": 547256.0,
      "text": "However, this work of reference is quite high-pitched."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 547280.0,
      "end_time": 550175.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s complex, and a lot of the terms are quite technical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 550200.0,
      "end_time": 554360.0,
      "text": "so the average person probably doesn&#39;t need to know at least a third of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 554960.0,
      "end_time": 557160.0,
      "text": "But the people of the Middle East"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 557400.0,
      "end_time": 561536.0,
      "text": "have been deprived of any form of what we know as civic education."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 561560.0,
      "end_time": 564335.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s part of our curriculum at school."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 564360.0,
      "end_time": 567456.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t really exist in that part of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 567480.0,
      "end_time": 569896.0,
      "text": "and I feel it&#39;s really the right of everybody"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 569920.0,
      "end_time": 572160.0,
      "text": "to know how these things work."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 572400.0,
      "end_time": 576656.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a good thing to think about producing a work of reference"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 576680.0,
      "end_time": 578335.0,
      "text": "for the average person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 578360.0,
      "end_time": 580496.0,
      "text": "and bearing in mind that now"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 580520.0,
      "end_time": 582696.0,
      "text": "we have a basis to work with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 582720.0,
      "end_time": 584856.0,
      "text": "but also we have technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 584880.0,
      "end_time": 589256.0,
      "text": "so we can reach out using telephone apps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 589280.0,
      "end_time": 591415.0,
      "text": "video, animation."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 591440.0,
      "end_time": 593736.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s all sorts of tools that can be used now"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 593760.0,
      "end_time": 596256.0,
      "text": "to communicate these ideas to people"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 596280.0,
      "end_time": 599000.0,
      "text": "for the first time in their own language."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 600200.0,
      "end_time": 602456.0,
      "text": "We hear a lot of misery about the Middle East."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 602480.0,
      "end_time": 605656.0,
      "text": "We hear the chaos of war. We hear terrorism."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 605680.0,
      "end_time": 611215.0,
      "text": "We hear about sectarianism and all this horrible negative news"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 611240.0,
      "end_time": 612896.0,
      "text": "that comes to us all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 612920.0,
      "end_time": 617776.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;re not hearing is what are the people, the everyday people, thinking?"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 617800.0,
      "end_time": 619400.0,
      "text": "What are they aspiring to?"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 619960.0,
      "end_time": 623880.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s give them the means, let&#39;s give them the words."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 624480.0,
      "end_time": 626696.0,
      "text": "The silent majority is silent"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 626720.0,
      "end_time": 628800.0,
      "text": "because they don&#39;t have the words."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 629200.0,
      "end_time": 631720.0,
      "text": "The silent majority needs to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 632440.0,
      "end_time": 635456.0,
      "text": "It is time to provide people with the knowledge tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 635480.0,
      "end_time": 637720.0,
      "text": "that they can inform themselves with."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 638920.0,
      "end_time": 642550.0,
      "text": "The silent majority does not need to be silent."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 642800.0,
      "end_time": 644376.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s help them have a voice."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 644400.0,
      "end_time": 645656.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 645680.0,
      "end_time": 650502.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}